---
title: Arrabbiata Prawn & Courgette Fusilli with Parmesan Cheese & Parsley
description: A seafood pasta is just the thing we need to make dinner time feel extra special. The tomato sauce is rich and aromatic, with an array of veggies and fragrant herbs. Fresh prawns are the finishing touch to this taste sensation!

*We’ve replaced the basil
in this recipe with parsley
due to local ingredient
availability. It’ll be just
as delicious, just follow
your recipe card!*
